<cb:div type="nanchuan-notes">
<head>漢譯南傳大藏經 註解</head>
<p>
<note n="0064001" resp="#resp1" place="foot text" type="orig" target="#nkr_note_orig_0064001">本文 sattaiṁsavasso 是 sattatiṁsavasse？</note>
<note n="0065002" resp="#resp1" place="foot text" type="orig" target="#nkr_note_orig_0065002">本文 Nāgadasassa ekâbhisekaṁ siñcayuṁ 是 Nāgadāse ekavīse bhisiñcayuṁ？</note>
<note n="0065003" resp="#resp1" place="foot text" type="orig" target="#nkr_note_orig_0065003">歐魯登貝克所見從十七年是有關阿婆耶之死後十七年空位之記事。得說明二四之數。</note>
<note n="0065004" resp="#resp1" place="foot text" type="orig" target="#nkr_note_orig_0065004"><space quantity="0"/></note>
<note n="0065005" resp="#resp1" place="foot text" type="orig" target="#nkr_note_orig_0065005">chāta（覆）善見律為車多迦（大正二四．六八七頁c）。</note>
<note n="0065006" resp="#resp1" place="foot text" type="orig" target="#nkr_note_orig_0065006">本文 velyaṭṭhi tayo 是 veḷuyaṭṭhi tayo？</note>
<note n="0066007" resp="#resp1" place="foot text" type="orig" target="#nkr_note_orig_0066007">就此等之文見巴利善見律（Samantap. Vol. I. p. 74 f）。見巴利大王統史一一．一〇以下，今參照此等譯出。</note>
<note n="0066008" resp="#resp1" place="foot text" type="orig" target="#nkr_note_orig_0066008"><space quantity="0"/></note>
<note n="0066009" resp="#resp1" place="foot text" type="orig" target="#nkr_note_orig_0066009">本文 ete aṭṭha 是 etā aṭṭha？</note>
<note n="0066010" resp="#resp1" place="foot text" type="orig" target="#nkr_note_orig_0066010">摩羅耶（Malaya）於此處謂錫蘭島內地之山脈地方。</note>
<note n="0066011" resp="#resp1" place="foot text" type="orig" target="#nkr_note_orig_0066011">本文 jātikaṁ 是 jātika？</note>
<note n="0066012" resp="#resp1" place="foot text" type="orig" target="#nkr_note_orig_0066012">本文 laddhaṁ mama puññakammasambhavaṁ 是 laddhaṁ mama passatha puññasambhavaṁ？</note>
<note n="0066013" resp="#resp1" place="foot text" type="orig" target="#nkr_note_orig_0066013">本文 me 是 ime？</note>
<note n="0066014" resp="#resp1" place="foot text" type="orig" target="#nkr_note_orig_0066014">未見之善友（adiṭṭhasahāya）雖未會見由書信而知會之友之意。</note>
<note n="0066015" resp="#resp1" place="foot text" type="orig" target="#nkr_note_orig_0066015">sāsanaṁ dhanaṁ 是 pasādhanaṁ dhanaṁ。</note>
<note n="0066016" resp="#resp1" place="foot text" type="orig" target="#nkr_note_orig_0066016">本文 utthehi kattāra 是 uṭṭhehi tāta？</note>
<note n="0067017" resp="#resp1" place="foot text" type="orig" target="#nkr_note_orig_0067017">本文 praṁcapabbataṁ 是 arantapabbataṁ？</note>
<note n="0067018" resp="#resp1" place="foot text" type="orig" target="#nkr_note_orig_0067018">本文 chattañ cāmarasaṅdhañ ca 是 chattaṁ cāmara-khaggañ, see Samantapasadikā（Siamese ed. I. 76）。</note>
<note n="0067019" resp="#resp1" place="foot text" type="orig" target="#nkr_note_orig_0067019">nandiyāvattaṁ 據 Mahāvaṁsa 之本文為右旋之螺。漢譯亦直譯為有「喜旋」之處。即指螺之右旋之形者。然今暫依據 Vinaya-ṭīka（Siamese ed. I. 248）因右旋顯示物之順當事者而珍重。次之化粧粉末（vaḍḍhamāna Skt. vardhamāna）漢譯有「樹文」。恐最初表示樹之紋理生長與生長有不可分之關係。依表示物之增加思是珍重樹之年輪或處女（Mahāvyutpatti XVIII. 81）。</note>
<note n="0067020" resp="#resp1" place="foot text" type="orig" target="#nkr_note_orig_0067020">此不要洗濯布即為火浣布（見和漢三才圖繪）。就此等之贈物名稱於一二下一七．八三以下被複說。</note>
<note n="0067021" resp="#resp1" place="foot text" type="orig" target="#nkr_note_orig_0067021">本文 abhovimaṁ vatthayugaṁ 是 adhavimaṁ vatthakotim？（XII. 2. XVII. 84 參照）然併在 vivaya-ṭikā 有 adhovinaṁ dussayugaṁ。</note>
<note n="0067022" resp="#resp1" place="foot text" type="orig" target="#nkr_note_orig_0067022">本文 dutiyam abhisiñcittha 是 dutiyâbhisekena（XVII. 87 參照）。</note>
<note n="0067023" resp="#resp1" place="foot text" type="orig" target="#nkr_note_orig_0067023">本文 tayo māse 是 toto māsaṁ。</note>
</p>
